description: This repository documents my learning journey in Full Stack Data Science with a focus on Generative AI and Agentic AI. It includes daily tasks, hands-on projects, and experiments using Python, machine learning, and modern AI frameworks. The work reflects both foundational concepts and advanced techniques applied in real-world scenarios.
Open source machine learning framework to automate text- and voice-based conversations: NLU, dialogue management, connect to Slack, Facebook, and more - Create chatbots and voice assistants

This project is an  end-to-end Machine Learning web application that predicts  medical insurance costs  based on user health data such as age, BMI, smoking habits, and region.   It combines Data Science , Flask Web Framework , Interactive Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS) , and  Docker for deployment  showcasing both  AI and DevOps skills.

A detailed educational article exploring how Streamlit revolutionizes AI app development. Learn how this Python framework bridges the gap between data science and usability, empowering anyone to deploy interactive machine learning models without front-end coding or complex infrastructure.
an intelligent cybersecurity solution that uses machine learning to automatically detect, analyze, and alert potential threats in real time.
Predictive Vulnerability Detection: Using machine learning models to predict potential vulnerabilities in Programming Languages based on SEcurity Feature Framework (SEFF) criteria
A universal machine learning force field framework

Space Labs AI presents: A radiation-tolerant machine learning framework enabling neural networks to operate reliably in space environments. Features adaptive protection, Reed-Solomon error correction, and breakthrough architecture optimizations that improve performance under radiation.

This repo contains machine learning and deep learning models for various problems, using frameworks like scikit-learn, TensorFlow, and PyTorch. It includes ML algorithms, neural networks, and notebooks demonstrating data preprocessing, model training, and evaluation.
Advanced multi-model deepfake detection framework combining ensemble machine learning with deep neural networks for robust image authentication and media forensics.
Machine learning framework for predicting NOx and O

credit-risk-ai-pro is a modular, configuration-driven framework for AI-based credit risk modeling, stress testing, and model governance. It integrates state-of-the-art machine learning and explainable AI techniques to build robust, interpretable, and regulatory-aligned financial risk models.

Cifer provides a decentralized AI development ecosystem with data-ownership proof on the Cifer blockchain, using a Privacy-Preserving Machine Learning (PPML) framework offers several methods for secure, private, collaborative machine learning Federated Learning and Fully Homomorphic Encryption

Artificial intelligence and machine learning landscape evolves, there are many tools and frameworks available for developers. Among these, Mediapipe stands out as a comprehensive solution for various computer vision tasks, including human pose estimation

Curated collection of essential books and learning resources for Machine Learning . Covers fundamental concepts, algorithms, and practical applications in Python with frameworks like TensorFlow and PyTorch. Suitable for all levels, from beginners to advanced practitioners. Contributions welcome!
Practical Machine Learning Framework for Designing and Predicting C-Amidated Antimicrobial Peptides

In this project, we developed a forecasting framework that outperforms Ternas baseline predictions by integrating statistical and machine learning models within a rolling forecasting pipeline, using ensemble averaging and systematic evaluation across multiple Italian regions
A framework which exploits temporal graphs, machine learning, and deep learning techniques for retrieving, modeling, and analyzing data of the Ethereum blockchain
Transformers: the model-definition framework for state-of-the-art machine learning models in text, vision, audio, and multimodal models, for both inference and training.
Using Convolutional Neural Networks and state-of-the-art Machine learning frameworks for real time clinical diagnosis
Predict football match outcomes using the W-5 Multi-Agent AI Consensus Framework, achieving high accuracy with a blend of AI and machine learning techniques.
Unified Machine Learning/Deep Learning demo repository combining most of the popular ML frameworks.
An open-source framework for training AI agents in realistic dogfight scenarios using reinforcement learning, JSBSim flight dynamics, and Azure Machine Learning integration.

This project presents SecureScan, a hybrid framework for secure QR code scanning that integrates traditional URL validation, blacklist detection, and machine learning-based malicious URL analysis. The system ensures protection against phishing, malicious websites, and security vulnerabilities. Developed as a Final Year Project 2025.
A machine learning framework for predicting and designing the mechanical properties of low-carbon steel.
Machine Learning based framework for estimation of Effective Population Size(Ne) from genetic summary statistics

QStruct is a scalable framework that integrates Hadoop, Spark, and Kafka with machine learning and quantum-inspired algorithms for RNA 3D structure prediction. It leverages HDFS for data storage, Spark for distributed training, and Kafka for real-time processing, enabling efficient, large-scale RNA analysis for drug discovery.
A customized autograd framework for machine learning

Python framework for building, validating, and backtesting quantitative trading strategies with machine learning, featuring robust data analysis, realistic backtesting, and comprehensive risk analytics.
A Machine Learning Framework for Comprehensive Classification of Plant Transcription Factors
Comprehensive tennis analytics and machine learning framework to quantify player performance, match dynamics, and tour-level insights.

This project addresses the challenge of creating an objective, data-driven system for quality assessment. By leveraging machine learning, we aim to uncover the key chemical drivers of wine quality and provide a framework for both automated quality prediction and market segmentation.
A hybrid optimization framework that integrates machine learning and optimization algorithms to improve couriertask allocation and routing efficiency in real-world conditions

This project implements a machine learning-based Digital Twin framework for the battery recycling industry. It integrates data from recycled battery bags and blackmass chemical analysis to simulate, predict, and optimize the recycling process.
A framework for encapsulating and representing detection results and metadata into interoperable records about analytics subjects that are detected by machine learning pipelines in the edge
Advanced Machine Learning Framework in Python, Rust & Go - A comprehensive ML library with scikit-learn-like API supporting classical ML and deep learning across three languages
A comprehensive machine learning project that predicts corporate bankruptcy by comparing four models, from a traditional financial formula to an advanced multi-modal deep learning architecture

AI Innovation at Google DevFest ATL 2025 This repository showcases our AI project developed for Google DevFest Atlanta 2025. The project integrates machine learning, real-time data processing, and intelligent automation to solve real-world challenges through innovative use of Google Cloud AI and open-source frameworks.
Machine Learning Framework for Protein-Protein Interaction Prediction
Efficient Real-time-Processing Driven TestingLibrary Framework, Leveraging Machine-Learning Intelligence for Scalable, Distributed, and Adaptive Automation Suite.

This project presents a comprehensive stock market analysis framework that integrates machine learning, deep learning, and reinforcement learning to enhance investment strategies and trading decisions.

A next-generation AutoML construction framework that lets developers, researchers, and ML engineers design, evolve, and orchestrate machine learning pipelines as modular systems  not pre-built black boxes.
A machine learning framework built from scratch with 68 algorithms spanning classical ML, clustering, dimensionality reduction, manifold learning, AutoML, and explainability.

This repository implements a Machine Translation system using a Sequence-to-Sequence (Seq2Seq) architecture with attention mechanism for translating English sentences to Hindi. Built using deep learning frameworks, the project includes data preprocessing, model training, evaluation, and inference scripts.

RESTful API for vector similarity search. It uses the Python web framework FastAPI and a REDIS vector database.  This accelerates machine learning workflows that require vector similarity search using classification models.
XGBoost-based machine learning framework to predict VM CPU demand in cloud data centers using Google Cluster Trace data, with SHAP analysis for model interpretability.
Machine Learning Testing dan Optimasi Framework untuk Prediksi komposisi Produk Fraksinasi Pada Industri Oleokimia
MetaXVP: An Interpretable Machine Learning Framework for Deep Insight into Variant Pathogenicity and VUS Classification

A full-featured MLOps framework built on Google Cloud Platform. This repository implements an end-to-end machine learning lifecycle with automated training, deployment, monitoring, and human-in-the-loop feedback.

A high-performance fraud analytics framework leveraging advanced ensemble learning and feature explainability for large-scale healthcare claims data. Integrates gradient boosting, random forests, and anomaly detection models with SHAP-based interpretability to uncover fraudulent behavioral patterns in real time.

Official code for a Ph.D. thesis predicting urban growth in Lucknow. This project develops a novel hybrid intelligence framework that integrates machine learning with Explainable AI (SHAP). It resolves the "black box" problem to create a transparent, reproducible, and highly accurate model for sustainable urban planning.
A multi-party collaborative machine learning framework

This project is a hands-on application of machine learning to solve a real-world problem: predicting laptop prices. It features a Random Forest Regressor model, trained on a dataset of laptop specifications, and deployed as a simple web application using the Flask framework. The entire workflow, from data cleaning in a Jupyter Notebook to function

Master's thesis codebase for evaluation of fusion strategies in clinical depression screening. Multimodal depression detection framework using Text, Audio, and Video modalities with Early and Late Fusion strategies. Implements Logistic Regression and XGBoost classifiers on E-DAIC dataset with SHAP and coefficient-based methods.

Reinforce4j is a Java library designed for implementing reinforcement learning algorithms, with a primary focus on Monte Carlo Tree Search (MCTS). It provides tools and frameworks for building agents that can learn to play games, demonstrated with examples like Tic-Tac-Toe and Connect 4. The library supports integration with machine learning models
Automated modeling and machine learning framework FEDOT
A comprehensive machine learning framework for quantitative trading strategies
Simple Framework to create game for my machine learning research testing AI
Hyrax - A framework for machine learning in astronomy

Promotion  Sensitive  Hierarchical Probabilistic  Forecasting  Demand is  an advanced  machine  learning  framework  designed to  accurately  forecast  Consumer  demand by  capturing  promotional  effects  hierarchical  sales  dependencies  uncertainty  distributions  across products regions time scales

I specialize in creating scalable and efficient solutions using Python and popular machine learning frameworks. The projects shared here represent real-world applicationsranging from predictive models and automation tools to web-integrated AI systems
Machine Learning framework for quantitative trading strategies with feature engineering, backtesting, and ensemble models
This project detects fraudulent transactions in a fintech dataset, using ensemble ML for anomaly detection. Align with operational risk frameworks. Use a credit card fraud dataset from Kaggle.

Bioinformatics and Machine Learning framework for in silico prediction of candidiasis-related microRNAs. Includes data processing, feature engineering, and ML models for miRNA-disease association prediction.

Flask is a lightweight, open-source Python web framework used in Data Science to deploy and manage data-driven applications. It offers a simple yet powerful structure for creating web apps and APIs that integrate with data analysis or machine learning models, providing flexibility for custom solutions.

A conceptual framework combining Machine Learning & Risk Scoring to automate alert triage.   Key Idea: AI model flags suspicious transactions before manual review.    Tools Used: SQL + Python + Power BI + ChatGPT.    Impact: 30% reduction in manual investigation time, improved detection accuracy.

DVC es una herramienta complementaria a Git que permite gestionar y versionar datos y modelos de aprendizaje automtico en proyectos de ciencia de datos. Es independiente del lenguaje o framework, lo que la hace verstil y adecuada para cualquier proyecto de Machine Learning.

A machine learning framework for simulating and predicting random walks. Includes parameterized bias sampling, enhanced feature engineering, multi-dimensional support, and real-world applications such as financial markets, IoT sensor drift, healthcare monitoring, and cybersecurity.

Machine learning framework for Real Madrid player performance prediction. Position-specific models (RF, XGBoost, NN) with SHAP analysis across 8 seasons. 98.7% R for forwards. Includes weighted scoring systems and Docker deployment. 5,737 matches analyzed.

An integrated multimodal machine learning framework that combines facial emotion recognition, heart rate variability (HRV)based stress detection, and PHQ-9 questionnaire analysis to provide holistic, real-time mental health assessment through a web interface.
:ocean: A built from scratch machine learning framework
Autonomous Trading Propagator orchestrates Machine Learning Model Integration across a Distributed Risk Governance Framework, ensuring Scalable Intelligent Optimization.
Hobby project - making my own machine learning framework with numPy exclusively, to learn different concepts. Inspiration from the Torch package.
ALF-T5 - Adaptive Language Framework for T5 is a Machine Learning framework for Neural Machine Translation Systems training and, subsequently, bidirectional translation.

Physarum-inspired machine learning framework to design optimal renewable energy networks using Tokyo metro data for training and Namibia for testing. Combines bio-inspired intelligence with geospatial datasets.

Portfolio Optimization is a data science project that creates investment portfolios to maximize returns and manage risk using mean-variance optimization and machine learning. It features customizable workflows and frameworks like PyPortfolioOpt, designed for finance students and early-career data scientists.

Tackled the challenge of predicting tip amounts for NYC Green Taxis using the CRISP-DM framework and k-NN regression modeling. Acting as Machine Learning Engineers hired by NYC's Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC), our mission was to help optimize driver income by forecasting tip behavior and enhancing service strategies.
Client Retention Strategy App - A comprehensive churn prediction and retention management platform featuring machine learning models, data processing pipelines, and project planning frameworks.

HybridLinkSim is a simulation framework for modeling, analyzing, and comparing Radio Frequency (RF) and optical communication links in space missions. It integrates atmospheric attenuation models, link budget analysis, and machine learningbased performance prediction across multiple orbital scenarios (LEO, GEO, and Lunar).

An experimental project integrating NLP and Machine Learning classification models to identify and categorize stress levels from text data  developed based on the Machine Learning Life Cycle (MLLC) framework.
Interactive learning experiences are enabled through intelligent PygameTutorials, leveraging frameworks and seamless machine learning integration for optimized deployment.
A unified framework for machine learning with time series
A differentiable ray tracer using the PyTorch machine-learning framework in Python.

A machine learning project that applies Vis-NIR spectral data to predict key plant nutrients using ensemble models within a stacked learning framework. This work demonstrates how data-driven methods can enhance agricultural productivity through scalable nutrient estimation.
ytopt: machine-learning-based autotuning and hyperparameter optimization framework using Bayesian Optimization

This repository offers a fully automated, object-oriented machine learning framework that providing a scalable framework for efficient model training, evaluation, and logging. Supporting various classification algorithms and requiring minimal coding (97% coding-free), it allows users to manage the entire process via command-line arguments.

This repository serves as a hub for my ML/AI explorations, implementations, and tutorials. It includes:   Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) projects  Machine Learning models for predictions and classifications  Deep Learning projects using frameworks like TensorFlow, PyTorch, and Hugging Face  Natural Language Processing (NLP) applications
Spatial EcoTyper is a machine learning framework for systematic identification of spatially distinct multicellular communities from single-cell spatial transcriptomics data.

Interpretable machine learning framework for thyroid disease diagnosis using ensemble stacking and feature selection methods. Incorporates SHAP and LIME to ensure model transparency and explainability.
gCoSRNA, a generalizable machine learning framework for predicting coaxial stacking in RNA junctions using only sequence and secondary structure information.

A Java-based Personality Detection System using the Tribuo ML framework. Trains and compares Logistic Regression, Random Forest, and XGBoost models to predict personality traits from behavioral data, deploying the best-performing model for accurate predictions.

Machine learning framework to predict ICU and hospital length of stay in infants with congenital heart disease undergoing cardiac surgery. Combines representation learning (MKL), clustering, and local models to provide interpretable, personalized predictions from perioperative data.
This project demonstrates a simple example of using machine learning in Rust with the Linfa framework. It trains a linear regression model to map input features to target values.

Official implementation of our paper "Unsupervised Active Learning via Natural Feature Progressive Framework", currently under review at IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence (TPAMI)

AI-powered system for early stroke prediction that combines machine learning, deep learning, and explainable AI techniques. This comprehensive framework enhances predictive accuracy while ensuring clinical interpretability and fairness in healthcare applications.
An Open Source Machine Learning Framework for Everyone

This repository contains practical code samples and exercises from "Hands-On Machine Learning with Scikit-Learn, Keras, and TensorFlow" by Aurelien Geron. Its designed as a hands-on companion for understanding and mastering machine learning concepts using Pythons most popular frameworks.
